snippet.title: Quality Dreams, Reasonably Priced - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
In Quality Dreams, Reasonably Priced you work as a body modification consultant in a dystopian future. 

Talk to clients, make recommendations, and decide how much to upsell them. Your choices will impact each of their lives. Balance helping others with earning enough to save your sick rabbit. 

And remember! You work on commission.

Wishlist here https://store.steampowered.com/app/3164710/Quality_Dreams_Reasonably_Priced/
